<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="either-adv">either <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'aɪðə(r)/    美 /'iðər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>也:</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It won't do them any good, but it won't do them any harm either.
这对他们没好处，但也没什么害处。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>A society cannot be successful if it throws tradition away, but it cannot be successful too if we do something to stop progress.  （2013 福建改 改错）  </li>
<li>Jane won't join us for dinner tonight and Tom won't <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ .  （2011 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. too → either  2. either  </p></div>